    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CZO Online - 这是一款战术多人第一人称射击游戏，玩家有机会使用武器库中的多种武器参与多人战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >享受经典游戏模式，例如：团队死亡竞赛、夺旗战、自由搏斗、反击、掩护点、枪战、炸弹拆除。与队友的合作和沟通将是获胜的关键！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras/6223c80785ce41f1d122c41b01430066.poster.avif?t=1739469976\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras/6223c80785ce41f1d122c41b01430066.webm?t=1739469976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras/6223c80785ce41f1d122c41b01430066.mp4?t=1739469976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras/104ee05d94d8dac940d291616e70ac33.avif?t=1739469976\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras_big/104ee05d94d8dac940d291616e70ac33.avif?t=1739469976 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>定制器：</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有武器都可以定制，包括刀、斧头和手榴弹。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras/aec887579785df7666cbac56b161f57f.poster.avif?t=1739469976\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras/aec887579785df7666cbac56b161f57f.webm?t=1739469976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras/aec887579785df7666cbac56b161f57f.mp4?t=1739469976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>能够使用汽车、重型战斗技术或呼叫支援：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras/daf67cbe2e01d28803ca7923e82cf0f3.avif?t=1739469976\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras_big/daf67cbe2e01d28803ca7923e82cf0f3.avif?t=1739469976 width=800 height=444 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>疯狂有趣的动态游戏玩法：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras/730662be48cbb73b4c1d6710c6d7b6b9.poster.avif?t=1739469976\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras/730662be48cbb73b4c1d6710c6d7b6b9.webm?t=1739469976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras/730662be48cbb73b4c1d6710c6d7b6b9.mp4?t=1739469976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras/a840c6539c945bf329fbf1e599d5dfe8.poster.avif?t=1739469976\" width=544 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras/a840c6539c945bf329fbf1e599d5dfe8.webm?t=1739469976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3075390/extras/a840c6539c945bf329fbf1e599d5dfe8.mp4?t=1739469976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>可能性：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 7 种游戏模式 [团队死亡竞赛、夺旗战、混战、反击战、掩护点、枪战、拆除炸弹]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 多人游戏（最多 20 名玩家）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 第一/第三人称视角</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 10 张地图</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 大量玩家和武器皮肤选择</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 约 37 种武器模型</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 支持车辆 [汽车、坦克]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 支持连杀 [直升机、无人驾驶飞机、导弹阵风]</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 部族系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 等级系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 进度系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 评级系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 高级 AI 机器人</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 好友系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 聊天系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 语音系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 装备系统</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 武器定制</p>",
